	<!-- EN: A lightweight but powerful fragmentation grenade, releasing a deadly storm of flechettes on detonation. -->
	<OuterRim_FragGrenade.description>A lightweight but powerful fragmentation grenade, releasing a deadly storm of flechettes on detonation.</OuterRim_FragGrenade.description>
	
	<!-- EN: A lightweight but powerful explosive, releasing a cloud of supercooled cryoban to freeze opponents solid. Does little direct damage by itself. -->
	<OuterRim_CryoBanGrenade.description>A lightweight but powerful explosive, releasing a cloud of supercooled cryoban to freeze opponents solid. Does little direct damage by itself.</OuterRim_CryoBanGrenade.description>
	
	<!-- EN: A lightweight but powerful pulse detonator, burning out its internal components to release an electromagnetic shockwave that can disable or even damage droids. -->
	<OuterRim_IonGrenade.description>A lightweight but powerful pulse detonator, burning out its internal components to release an electromagnetic shockwave that can disable or even damage droids.</OuterRim_IonGrenade.description>
	
	<!-- EN: A lightweight but powerful plasma detonator, releasing a burst of superheated gas to inflict tremendous burns on anyone nearby. -->
	<OuterRim_PlasmaGrenade.description>A lightweight but powerful plasma detonator, releasing a burst of superheated gas to inflict tremendous burns on anyone nearby.</OuterRim_PlasmaGrenade.description>
	
	<!-- EN: A lightweight but powerful sonic generator, burning out its internal components to release a shockwave that causes blunt force trauma to all in the radius. -->
	<OuterRim_SonicGrenade.description>A lightweight but powerful sonic generator, burning out its internal components to release a shockwave that causes blunt force trauma to all in the radius.</OuterRim_SonicGrenade.description>
	
	<!-- EN: A lightweight but nonlethal detonator, emitting a bright flash and loud sound to stun targets, useful when attempting to take someone in alive and unharmed. -->
	<OuterRim_StunGrenade.description>A lightweight but nonlethal detonator, emitting a bright flash and loud sound to stun targets, useful when attempting to take someone in alive and unharmed.</OuterRim_StunGrenade.description>
	
	<!-- EN: A lightweight but tremendously powerful explosive, capable of inflicting terrible harm on anything caught in its area of effect. -->
	<OuterRim_ThermalDetonator.description>A lightweight but tremendously powerful explosive, capable of inflicting terrible harm on anything caught in its area of effect.</OuterRim_ThermalDetonator.description>
	
